            "name": "Grab",
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "After the python bites a creature with its jaws, it can attempt an Athletics check against the target's Fortitude DC (Fortitude DC = a target's Fortitude save bonus + 10). If successful, the character is grabbed, and the python cannot bite anyone again until it wraps up the creature in its coils. The DC to Escape is 16.",
